databaseoperation.name: updateNiprBusinessAddressInAgencyBusinessAdress
databaseoperation.sqlstmt: SELECT ISNULL(UPPER(PA.Address_Line_1),'') as Address_Line_1,ISNULL(UPPER(PA.Address_Line_2),'') as Address_Line_2,ISNULL(UPPER(PA.Address_Line_3),'') as Address_Line_3,ISNULL(UPPER(PA.City),'') as City , st.state_id as state_id ,PA.Zip as Zip ,PA.Country_Code as country_code FROM niprone.PDB_Address PA with(nolock) inner join state_lku st with(nolock) on st.abbreviation = PA.NPN_State_Code WHERE pdb_report_id in(select top 1 pdb_report_id from agency_master where agency_id = #agency_id#) AND PA.NPN_State_Code=(SELECT TOP 1 sl.abbreviation FROM [niprone].[npn_licenses] nl with(nolock) INNER JOIN state_lku sl with(nolock) on sl.state_id=nl.state_id WHERE is_resident='Y' AND transaction_id in( select top 1 pdb_report_id from agency_master with(nolock) where agency_id = #agency_id#) ) AND PA.AddressCode =1
